       Megatron turned to look at Killfest. What was he doing? Was he out of 
his mind? Megatrons troops were all over the bridge and he just plainly tries 
to take command? Thats not the Predacon way...
       Locking his shoulder into place, Megatron releases four powerful shots 
from his tail cannon. He was sorry to see it end like this, but if he missed 
Rampage, Tankkor, and Hell Beast, who also took aim, would certianly pick him 
off. 
       "Get that body to the boiler room....we can use it to power the ship." 
Tarantulas said, just before MEgatron took that fateful shot at Killfest.

--part1_c8.d9ede0c.27583fb2_boundary
